# Generator scratch files. Each sub-folder under _workspace and _bookshelf is
# an isolated tsp-client output used only for per-sub-project compilation
# validation by the generator. They share AssemblyName=Azure.AI.Discovery with
# the shipping src/Azure.AI.Discovery.csproj, which would collide in CI's
# recursive csproj enumeration. The shipping package consumes the generated
# .cs files directly via globs in src/Azure.AI.Discovery.csproj, so the sub-
# package csproj/sln files have no role in the shipped artifact.
_workspace/**/*.csproj
_workspace/**/*.sln
_bookshelf/**/*.csproj
_bookshelf/**/*.sln
